{"tid":640021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為：Kirin處理器不外銷，不會像 Samsung 那樣","createTime":"2018-04-24T03:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T07:04:49.000Z","uid":20815,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"a60385f99032748af310253d2c91606d191c91fd","tid":640021,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T03:10:56.000Z","msg":"在 4月17日召開的華為分析師大會上，董事長徐直軍表示，自家的 Kirin 處理器目前沒有任何想法和計劃對外銷售。 華為公司並不打算依靠處理器作為收益的一部分。自己做處理器是為了更好體現產品差異化，提升競爭力，暫無對外銷售 Kirin 處理器的想法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XrcqXzlrO9OJXfZL421p2A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/qooah.tw/7149f71417434379dc0fc3bdd7fcc959\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXrcqXzlrO9OJXfZL421p2A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fqooah.tw%2F7149f71417434379dc0fc3bdd7fcc959&h=153632bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近幾年來，Kirin 處理器活躍於華為和榮耀的旗艦系列產品， Mate 10 系列以及 P20 系列上都配置了業內首款搭載獨立人工智能處理單元的 Kirin 970 。但並不是都用 Kirin 處理器，偶爾也會使用高通和 MTK。多處理器供應的戰略會繼續堅持，這樣才能確保智能終端業務的發展。多元化是世界的主流，如果不保持競爭，萬一某一天落後市場，後果不堪設想。<br />\n<br />\n雖然自產處理器，但其他智能終端核心元器件，類似屏幕、存儲等，並不會全方位去佈局。徐直軍表示，華為的戰略很是與盟友共同進步，推動發展，做好自己擅長的事，而不會像 Samsung 那樣去全方面定位，反而會顧此失彼。商業模式多種多樣，但適合自己的才是做最好的。<br />\n<br />\n對於近期中美貿易戰，徐直軍表示與其胡亂猜測，不如做好本職工作，以更好的服務留下客戶，如此才能生存發展下去。「不如把時間和精力花在打造更好的產品去服務客戶，有些事情放下了反而輕鬆。 」徐直軍說。<br />\n<br />\n此文章原刊於 <a href=\"http://Qooah.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FQooah.com&d=vtPIsuv%2BIxLerqTTrvhoOsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e575127f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Qooah.com</a><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA-kirin%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%96%E9%8A%B7-%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E5%83%8F-samsung-%E9%82%A3%E6%A8%A3-134547246.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA-kirin%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%2599%25A8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%258A%25B7-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2583%258F-samsung-%25E9%2582%25A3%25E6%25A8%25A3-134547246.html&d=vtPIsuv%2BIxLerqTTrvhoOsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=4d1759a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA-kirin%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%96%E9%8A%B7-%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E5%83%8F-samsung-%E9%82%A3%E6%A8%A3-134547246.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我好撚想用呀屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f892d500f38f72fd4750eec2422f0759fe7cf30","tid":640021,"uid":44171,"like":51,"dislike":2,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T03:16:13.000Z","msg":"咪又係台積電代工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ced8ae6239a613398cc6c8ae70b3f607dc6d60","tid":640021,"uid":35667,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T03:16:54.000Z","msg":"華為肯賣既話蘋果肯定買黎用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab10376cb633c10d7bcddc0d5ab40c51c911995","tid":640021,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T03:21:42.000Z","msg":"唔外銷得架"},{"pid":"0b28a00eeda5d6fd761d784fff3ca4c772509ee9","tid":640021,"uid":49316,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T03:22:12.000Z","msg":"支那又贏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61ab50464b8c695a624e40c1fbcf53710667988","tid":640021,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"qooah<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e851bd9073f6750ebfc764c88a59